                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1429" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MIS-0077</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8777 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机场运营管理信息化的破冰之旅——武汉天河机场运营管理信息系统的自主开发之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Ice-breaking Trip of information technology in Airport operations management ——Independent Explo</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李航，余新宇等</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国民航大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">武汉天河机场</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">自主开发；运营管理信息系统；可持续信息化建设；天河机场；IT自包</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Self-development; Operations MIS; Sustainable IT Construction; Tian he Airport; IT Insuring</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例主要讲述了从2000年以来，武汉天河机场在生产运营管理信息化建设过程中，始终坚持“以我为主、自主创新”的发展历程。站在天河机场IT开发团队的视角，以事件发展的时间顺序，分别从跟踪学习、自我认识、路径设计、技术选择、持续完善共五个阶段，展现了机场业在运营管理信息化发展过程中面临的困境、坚持自主开发的可行性与必要性、自主开发过程中的难点与解决之道、技术选择的战略意义、管理信息系统持续完善的必要性以及自主开发形式在这方面的先天优势。天河机场在机场运营管理信息化的成功探索，为整个民航业以及机场这类专业化程度高、技术密集型同时相对小众的特殊企业，提供了信息化建设可鉴之处；某种程度上也代表着正在形成的一种企业信息化趋势。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Since 2000, Wuhan Tianhe Airport has always adhered to the development of “self-centered, self-innovation” throughout the IT construction process of production and operations management. Standing on Tianhe Airport IT development team’s perspective, this case shows some research values from five stages which are learning tracking, self-awareness, path design, technology selection and continuous improvement. The research values above can be summarized as predicament of airport industry in IT development of operation management, feasibility and necessity of self-development, difficulties in the process of self-development and solution, strategic significance of technology options, necessity of MIS’s improvement and inherent advantages of self-development. Tianhe Airport’s successful exploration provides an enlightenment of IT construction for the entire aviation industry and such high degree of specialization and technology-intensive while relatively small minority of special enterprise. To some extent, it also represents an emerging trend of corporation information.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2007</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理信息系统》、《ERP》、《IT项目管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业信息化</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013-11</td>
                            </tr>
